<br>
Looking about, she nods quietly to herself and leaves the way she came.<br>
<br>
The letter:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>To the Harvesters of Darkness:<br>
<br>
My name is Chaitra Sa'Diablo.  I am a Khati Sha in training from Shar Vahl.  Several of you have met me, as I can often be found in company with Chaes L'Cassiline, who is a childhood friend.<br>
<br>
It is my wish to seek a place within your hall.  I have studied you all from afar these past weeks, and you seem to be an interesting group.  I would like to get to know you better.  <br>
<br>
Should you wish a meeting, I am staying at the Shadeling Inn, within Shadowhaven.  You can leave any replies with the innkeeper.  <br>
<br>
Farewell, for now, <br>
<br>
Chaitra Sa'Diablo<br>
Khati Sha <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bharvestersofdarkness.showUserPublicProfile?gid=chaeslcassiline@harvestersofdarkness>Chaes LCassiline</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br> <font color=#A8A8A8>(8/16/03 9:27 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Khati Sha</span><hr size=1> Chaes watches quietly from his usual corner near the doorway as Chaitra slips in, tilting his head curiously to the side. A hand drops down to curb Sascha's excitement at seeing Chaitra, to keep her from ruining his concealment.<br>
<br>
  Narrowed eyes watched as Chaitra dropped the letter onto the desk. He had no right to look within it, but he could guess well enough it's contents.<br>
<br>
  Watching Chaitra leave, Chaes shifted his dark green steel vambraces, tightening the straps idly as he thought. Finally, when he knew Chaitra would be out of earshot, he murmured.. &quot;Now what is she up to..&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/bharvestersofdarkness.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ankhami>Ankhami</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Yath'tallar of Vengance<br>
